race.comment: SUPER TWENTY THREE (1) is another winning hope for jockey Ryan Wiggins. Made significant late ground last start to find third over 1000m at Townsville, and had been knocking on the door there prior in stronger. Boasts a sound record at this track and trip and will go close. COPPABELLA ROAD (3) showed good early muster and fought on to finish second last start over 1000m at Townsville. Will push forward and has winning claims. THREEBROTHERS (5) comes out of the same races at Townsville and has been within range. He's in the mix as well. RARE AND RELIABLE (6) switched yards and needed the first-up outing at Townsville. Has a wide gate but is proven second-up and will be running into it.
